{
  "stem": "3964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Mail was intercepted.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we didn't have a radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was no telephone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Things were really pretty rotten, particularly for a 14-year-old boy who wants to conquer the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I knew what the situation was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I knew it was bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And aside from praying, saying I'll pray every day, there was very little we thought we could do to remedy the situation.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My father was still going to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And as-- when I came back to Gemunden in-- in-- in '40, I had to go back to work with him again, and again, carrying bricks.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And this was an ongoing thing-- just to be able to get rations, get food and not to be bothered.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They had to get away from Gemunden.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Things sort of-- you know, there-- there-- there's a time in life when you learn to live with your misery.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I guess that's where we had arrived-- all of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We were helpless-- nothing we could do to remedy the situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There was no help from the outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We knew that other Jewish communities were suffering as badly as we did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Although we heard that in the southern part of Germany, things weren't as bad as they were by us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But when you think you are-- you're-- you're badly off-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --and are-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --satisfied with your lot-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --you don't realize how well you are off when things got worse, which was in December of 1941.",
      "word_count": 46
    }
  ],
